</dd></dl><p><b>CERTTRANSDBATTRIBUTE Structures (variable):</b> An
array of <b>CERTTRANSDBATTRIBUTE</b> structures. These structures MUST be
contiguous and MUST NOT be padded. All <span><a href="c6451297-197d-4b4b-b786-3f3187b67b8f#gt_108a1419-49a9-4d19-b6ca-7206aa726b3f" data-linktype="relative-path">attribute</a></span> headers
MUST appear prior to any attribute data, which appears in the attribute data
byte array at the end of the packet.</p><dl>
<dd>
